> Deprecated resource

This resource is deprecated.

The updated version of this resource can be found here: [Document Templates Resource Reference](/doxee-platform/docs/document-templates-resource-reference).

## Description
The **Document template&nbsp;**resource allows to&nbsp;manage Infinica templates. You can use this resource in combination with the On-Demand Workflows Compose Documents tasks.

## Additional creation parameters
None.

## Resource editor
None.

## Release parameters
![](data:image/png;base64,)

Section

Field

Description

**Configuration**

**Summary**

Brief description of the release

**Template**

**URL**

Enter the URL representing the template identity in the Infinica repository.

## Deploy parameters
![](data:image/png;base64,)

Section

Field

Description

**Configuration**

**Release**

Select a release&nbsp;of the resource from the drop-down menu.

**Tenant**

Select the tenant&nbsp;on which you want to deploy the resource from the drop-down menu.

> Tip

Click **Publish** to publish the release on the tenant.

Click **Deploy** to publish and enable the release on the tenant.
